item.description: The New Home of Sensorgnome.org The sensorgnome project is in the process of moving to this new site. Announcements will be posted to the sensorgnomads google group For now, documentation is still available at the original sensorgnome.org site, hosted by Acadia University. Sponsors The sensorgnome project thanks Compudata.ca for contributing the hosting for this site, and for donating a portion of each unit sold to help us support and develop the platform.
